author: Briana Domjen
title: Nicole’s new jewellery has a solid gold price
text:
NICOLE Trunfio only recently made a foray into the world of jewellery design, but the ambitious model clearly has high hopes for her brand, selling the pieces for a small fortune.
The model’s Trunfio Universe range offers bracelets, rings and necklaces for prices on a par with that of high-end, luxury designers, suggesting her anticipated audience are the likes of Kim Kardashian and Beyonce .
One of Trunfio’s 18-carat rose gold diamond bangles is priced at $29,000, while a simple rose gold shooting star ring retails for $1248.
Supermodel Nicole Trunfio Launches her jewellery range Trunfio Universe Even Trunfio’s followers found the prices hard to stomach, with fan Loretta-mi writing, “Great stuff but $17,000 for a bracket (sic)???. You serious,” on the mother-of-one’s Instagram page.
Trunfio created the 92-piece range while pregnant with first son Zion.
“While enjoying pregnancy I spent my time building Trunfio Universe, making it special, sentimental and as unique as it could possibly be, with the intention to inspire women all over the world,” Trunfio wrote in a press release. “I am so excited.”
 There is no denying the range is of a high quality, with the pieces handcrafted by the artisans of the House Of Cerrone using the finest 18K gold or platinum and VS2 E-F white diamonds.
However, whether there will be a market for Trunfio’s inspired range is yet to be seen.
